content.html: I’m so proud that I got to watch this thing grow from an idea in the heads of #GarthEnnis, @DarickR + @therealKripke to a full-fledged show complete with an AMAZING fan base. Thank you for making that happen. You’re incredible and we’re forever grateful. #JusticeForTimothy (3/3)
